Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. There's nothing\Nmore to it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize to everyone. I don't\Nthink there's anything else I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, you weren't exactly\Nthe right person for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's remarkable that\Nyou've done this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of some way\Nto deal with it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if it does go well, it probably\Nwon't go in the direction you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:21.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Send
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:22.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sent
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here:\NSorry to bring this up out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,M-e-♪: Sorry, there's no getting\Naround the time and distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:32.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Given the situation,\Nthere's nothing you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:34.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,M-e-♪: It's a request from my\Ndear {\i1}kohai{\i0}. I wish I could do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:42.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any other ideas?\NAbout anyone who would be able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,M-e-♪: Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:45.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,M-e-♪:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here: Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,M-e-♪: I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:56.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,M-e-♪: They may not be much help,\Nbut depending on how you use them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone who could dance for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:04.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you think you\Ncan come on that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: I'll definitely be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:10.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: I made a mistake. I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:13.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here:\NI will be very pleased if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:16.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here:\NI'll send you the time and place later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: I very munich look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: That's munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:21.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here:\NYou might already know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here:\Nbut you don't have to convert to kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here:\NJust go ahead and hit 'Enter'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: Are you surge?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:37.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: Ah, you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here:\NOkay, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please insert name here:\NOh, and as long as you're at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,you can invite your friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:49.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,L: Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the Classic Lit Club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be delighted if you brought\Nall the club members with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I scowled at the wind blowing\Nat my window of boredom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:10.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I could turn away\Nthe awkwardness I was feeling{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:18.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:23.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I nod noncommittally at today\Nas I hold it in my hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:29.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}projecting myself a little exaggeratedly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:34.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get the feeling that\Nsomething is about to change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all because of you\Ncalling out to my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:46.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Peeking up at cloudy skies,\NI sense what's coming{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:54.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's reach out our hands\Nwith courage stronger than ever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:59.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light and shadow are both still far off{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:05.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but even so, we want to know\Nthe reason for this kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:13.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go look now, beyond the brilliance\Nthat goes by nobody's name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:25.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}before it all becomes a thing of the past{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Looks like he made the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on reaching the finals!\NMizutani Sho, 100m breaststroke
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:39.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Go To the Screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I have any kind of talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like Fukube Satoshi\Ndoesn't have any natural gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to think that I'm a late bloomer,\Nbut those chances are slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, "database"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do take pride in that,\Nwhen it comes to intellectual matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even if I polish that up,\NI'll never be a quiz show king.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. And I couldn't be\Nmore envious, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, there's more than\Njust being envious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such as?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geniuses don't get to choose to live normal\Nlives like we do, even if they wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see some appeal\Nin living a normal life, Hotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, that's probably true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if you're going to be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Fukube Satoshi\Ndoesn't have any special talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd like to hold off on whether\Nthat's true for Oreki Hotaro, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think I don't lead a normal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you don't observe\Npeople closely enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I'd like to hold\Noff on evaluating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, shouldn't we be hurrying along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka will be all over us if we're\Nlate to the editorial meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Pete's sake, it's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again,\Ntrying to laugh it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's not here yet. I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The disparity here is\Npretty awful, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the difference in your behaviors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's go to a screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A video movie that was produced\Nby Class 2-F is being shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone who is in that class,\Nand she wants to hear what we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were talking about that,\Nwhich is why I am late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of movie is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, she said it was a mystery movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Audiovisual Classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to take you up on your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I appreciate you coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. Thank you for\Naccepting my invitation today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibara Mayaka-{\i1}san{\i0}, Fukube Satoshi-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nand Oreki Hotaro-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the other members of\Nthe Classic Lit Club that I am in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure. I am Irisu Fuyumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then it {\i1}is {\i0}you, Irisu-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I'd seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the culture festival planning\Ncommittee at the end of June.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mediating that dispute between\NLight Music Club and the Drama Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was truly something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine, Satoshi complimenting\Nsomeone so openly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I still don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0}, how do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family and the Irisu family\Nare on close terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we were little,\Nshe has been there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being an old and established\Nfamily sounds like a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, this is the movie\Nthat our class produced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to watch it,\Nand give me your candid opinion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to watch it and\Ngive you our opinions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something unusual about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we don't like it, you're not\Ngoing to re-shoot anything, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want us to publicize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't understand why\Nyou're showing it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a legitimate question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right that there's no meaning\Nin having you just watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it would be more\Nefficient if you watched it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More efficient?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our video movie doesn't have a title yet.\NThe working title is "Mystery."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the movie is over, there is something\NI would like to ask you, so be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get started.\NGood hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The volunteers of Class 2-F,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having decided to participate\Nin the Kanyasai,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and requiring material from the\NNarakubo area for their display,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are now heading to the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamanishi Midori
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugimura Jiro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Almost there.\NLess than five more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we heard you say that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Senoue Mamiko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Konosu Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuta Takeo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty tough going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hot, and I'm getting tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one who's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:10.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito Takeo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems about right, for an\Nindependent production.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it.\NThat's Narakubo over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Looks like it was worth it\Nto come here for material.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, let's secure\Na place to sleep tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll gather our material!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, over there is\Na good place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting kind of a\Nbad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mansion mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mansion mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof seems secure enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to sleep here!\NThere's glass scattered about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a place to stay\Nbefore it gets dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a floorplan over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A floorplan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and look around inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Isn't that dangerous?!\NAnd it's probably locked, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm sure there are keys.\NEh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that an office?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think those are the master keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have them getting lost.\NWe should leave them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are. We should be able to\Nlook everywhere with all of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go around looking\Nfor rooms we can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm!\NMm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this were real, don't you\Nthink they'd all stick together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's about to happen. I'd bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's {\i0}the one who talked to {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident happened soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were pieces of a broken\Nmirror scattered about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use it unless we clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. We found the same sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sugimura! How about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fairly clean in here. We might\Nbe able to use it. I'm coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kaito-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still looking around?\NWell, okay. Let's all go get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sitting room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down the wing, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No unauthorized personnel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't open. It's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get the master keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised she can get so\Nemotionally attached to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh? It isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the video there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is\Nthe culprit behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shosho {\i0}('Heat's End')\NFor the sunshine easeth,\Nand blue skies begin their withdrawl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:31.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will explain everything in turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but first, I want you to tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Technically speaking, what do\Nyou think of this video?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can be honest,\NI think it's pretty clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, as well. No matter how much\Npassion someone puts into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without any technical skill,\Nthe outcome will be obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that okay, for what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think it is good enough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's okay to indulge\Na world of self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying that its quality\Nis intrinsically important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what is the vital issue\Nconcerning this project?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that it isn't finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Not even we can\Nbe satisfied with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The video is shot on a unique location,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can only shoot it during summer\Nvacation, but it still isn't finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the shooting not go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shooting went as scheduled,\Nand was supposed to finish next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The script.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongo Mayu, the only girl in the class\Nwho has ever drawn any manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was delegated to provide the\Nscript for a one-hour movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongo did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when she had written as far\Nas you saw here, she took ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not saying you want {\i1}us {\i0}to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, getting back to my first question,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who do you think the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongo took ill just as we were\Ngetting to the resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone watching this should be able\Nto deduce who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are there really going\Nto be enough clues included
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a script written by an amateur?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be okay. She has\Nstudied a lot of mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She followed the Ten Commandments,\Nthe Nine Propositions, and the 20 Rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moses's Ten Commandments?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Knox's Ten Commandments.\NThe Nine Propositions and 20 Rules
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are all rules stipulating what\Nmust happen in a detective novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In other words, the key to solving\Nthe crime must be presented fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind, who do you\Nthink the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This {\i0}is what she meant by "Good hunting"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at providing the "who."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A database doesn't give those answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not so sure I\Ncould do it, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone that I suspect, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was just thinking that\Nthis is your territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being the detective. Wow,\Nwhat a disgusted-looking face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't watching that seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's have\Nher show it to us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind just your opinion.\NFeel free to keep it casual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Then I think\Nit was Yamanishi-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she had a bad attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irisu-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, why don't\N{\i1}you {\i0}consider who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know very little about mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why didn't you stop them from\Nusing a mystery as your subject matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't a part of the\Nproject at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got back from Hokkaido,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and jumped into sort this all\Nout the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had been involved from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt the project would\Nhave moved forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, lastly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why did you call on us,\Nthe Classic Lit Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, there's my\Nacquaintance with Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that, I heard all about\Nthat {\i1}Hyouka {\i0}business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she hear about it from Itoigawa-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I agreed to straighten\Nthis out, I remembered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that maybe you could\Nserve as my detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need you\Nexpecting anything of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I thought this\Nmight be an unwelcome request.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus concludes this screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I appreciate you coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will become of the ending, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I'll give it my effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm also prepared if it\Nends up being unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a tragedy to\Nleave this video unfinished!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\i0}can't bear it? It's {\i1}Irisu\N{\i0}that can't bear it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, having it unfinished would\Nleave a bad aftertaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And all of you got\Ntogether to make it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more... What's more,\Nwhat would make Hongo-{\i1}san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go so far as to diminish\Nboth her trust and health
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to give up writing the\Nscript halfway through?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am curious about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help her out, Hotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not doing anything anyway, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}, let's do this.\NLet's avenge Hongo-{\i1}san{\i0}'s death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongo isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may, Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we accept, and can't figure out\Nwho the culprit is, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow down and beg forgiveness\Nfrom everyone in Class 2-F?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take on that\Nkind of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you were to take on\Nroles as observers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd listen to our class's\Nprospective detectives,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then offer your viewpoints.\NHow about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all, then, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irisu-{\i1}senpai {\i0}is well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her family runs the general hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? An heiress to\Na big-time hospital, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the only thing\NIrisu-{\i1}senpai {\i0}is known for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a nickname.\NWhat would you guess it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Empress."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she, sadistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that would be a "Queen."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I salute you for knocking\Ndown what I set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes without saying that she is pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I hear she's also good at\Npushing people to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that everyone around\Nher ends up being her pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho? Isn't that something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, the Empress went to\Nthe trouble to give us an audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd like it if we all adopted\Nour own symbols, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Symbols?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, Mayaka's could\Nbe "Justice," maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a toss-up between that and "Judgment."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tarot cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Fuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}, what would you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking "The Fool."\NNah, maybe "The Magician."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you be the Fool, Chitanda-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right. Now that you\Nmention it, maybe I am the Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be one of my shortcomings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one is obvious. "Strength."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that right? I\Nwould think "The Star."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, definitely Strength.\NIt's perfect for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. That doesn't sound like a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. I came to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.\NMorning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we are going to see someone\Nwho will show us to the detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can listen to what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you manage to arrange this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Via chat. There is a chatroom on\Nthe Kamiyama High School homepage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where only students are allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they have that? Show me sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Classic Lit Club room?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Are you from Class 2-F?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name is Eba Kurako.\NIt is nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that Irisu has\Ntold you about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but today, I will be introducing\Nyou to our detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-{\i1}chan{\i0}, are those snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Today I have some\Nchocolates that we received.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that we could all\Nshare them as we talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brain doesn't work as well\Nwhen you're hungry, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of deductions\Nwe're going to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you looking forward to this, Hotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all sure are enjoying yourselves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we going to hear from?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assistant director,\Nthe prop man, and the publicist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? By the way, Eba-{\i1}senpai{\i0},\Nwhat are you in charge of?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not involved in the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly an answer after my own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eba-{\i1}san{\i0}, were you close with Hongo-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I am just curious as to what\Nkind of person wrote the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no-nonsense and meticulous,\Nwith a strong sense of responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kind to a fault, and delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, movie production\Nhas been shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there will probably be\Nno one else coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These three are our detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:04.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tonight it turns to love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:08.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meet me in a pleasant dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:12.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make sure that you find me, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:17.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our snooze-time date{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.11,0:24:38.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heat of your budding warmth troubles me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.95,0:24:48.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you understand how I feel yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.38,0:24:55.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There isn't supposed to be\Nany significance in your glance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.89,0:25:01.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, it's the same one\Nyou give all your friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.23,0:25:06.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tiny wishing star fading\Ninto the morning light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.98,0:25:11.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the magic it works during the night\N(I wish you would notice){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.94,0:25:15.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tonight it turns to love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:18.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meet me in a pleasant dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.74,0:25:22.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make sure that you find me, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:28.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our snooze-time date{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "The Case of the\NFuruoka Deserted Village Murder."
